      "shortDescription": "Post-(Rock/Metal) (Shoe/Black)-gaze one man band. 8 releases since 2012 spanning blackgaze, shoegaze, slowcore, ambient, and psychedelic.",
      "description": [
        "Post-(Rock/Metal) (Shoe/Black)-gaze one man band from Mexico City. Active since 2012, Dotzd is Ashel's primary solo vehicle for exploring the duality of opposites — day and night, change and the eternal constant. All songs written, performed, produced, mixed, and mastered by Ashel.",
        "The sound spans blackgaze, shoegaze, slowcore, psychedelia, ambient, and noise — whatever it takes to express the feeling of duality that is always a constant in life. \"Tempo\" was produced at Echo Bravo Studio. \"Empero\" features Carlo Ixcamparij on drums, marking the first collaboration on a Dotzd release."
      ],
      "members": [
        {
          "name": "Ashel",
          "role": "Guitars, Bass, Vocals, Drum Programming"
